<plot>A cruel and tender look at a series of British families who have chosen to live in France. The films explore the unspoken tensions and underlying issues common to these peculiar immigrants. With a light-hearted approach the director raises some universal questions: how hard is it to live far from one's home country ? What risks do you run trying to start life afresh ? How to adapt ?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?229610</url></doc>
